### S48 Acceptance — Implemented & Covered

**PASS.** The helper closes the gap that S47 left static: every frontend labor-report dropdown type is now driven through the real Chrome export button, validated via real xlsx parsing (ExcelJS), and confirmed via the actual `react-hot-toast` `[role="status"]` success container. The shape is clean, the existing tests still pass, and no regressions are introduced.
